{"tid":1278200,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒撚放暑假] [live?]日本由南玩到北","createTime":"2019-07-02T11:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T11:01:00.000Z","uid":118069,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b9e8c16c43820a4254e0ddd7b6d86479cc0308","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"首先， 識我勿起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的， 天氣開始炎熱了， 所以買左張機票去石垣島感受下有幾熱<br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n聽講係指定動作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgoTPdX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgoTPdX.jpg&h=550e0bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2個鐘左右就到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25ELFmN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25ELFmN.jpg&h=735de0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n輕鬆入境<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xg9f2Aj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXg9f2Aj.jpg&h=e74914a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭巴士去到總站，行去hostel諗住放低行李先食野， 點知&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qUzyJe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qUzyJe.jpg&h=e1187409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯有拖住個喼去食飯。 到達日本第一餐， 食邊銀食堂， 其實可以話係中式野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R7R9630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR7R9630.jpg&h=9d2abc80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫左杯好貴嘅芒果汁同撈麵， 佢d食物其實幾一般， 但加左佢d辣油之後， 成個層次唔同晒， 超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jKsdPhX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjKsdPhX.jpg&h=3aa5345b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VcVyPhW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVcVyPhW.jpg&h=6e2b4ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完再去check-in， 繼續I&rsquo;m out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亂行之下去左blue seal食雪糕， blue seal係沖繩好出名， 通街都係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UeFbAZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUeFbAZc.jpg&h=fa4c45a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於check-in到， 入左房之後試下佢張床， 點知一試完已經7點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來想去join觀星船， 唯有明天請早<br />\n<br />\n訓醒餓餓地去搵食，見到有間食扒，入去試下<br />\n叫左個rump steak set，今日平1000yen<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RiSmm0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRiSmm0J.jpg&h=786da9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙律唔錯，飯同湯都無限refill<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZ6KjNn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZ6KjNn.jpg&h=a7ab2dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主菜到，老細無問我要幾成熟，不過煮到好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yjf7hAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyjf7hAZ.jpg&h=2c2a6f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sqmyc9i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqmyc9i.jpg&h=2dc28c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽就返房搞行程，Day 1 完"},{"pid":"9dfe2588a0953f3b64aa50f87c25953d97d5b68b","tid":1278200,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"留名學野<br />\n由南到北?<br />\n唔會北到北海道下話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d643c5023f79e68dc7ff03a57b77fe2e7c044a1f","tid":1278200,"uid":149912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6416be8df7bd6c35a87e006b0ac0313eedb4cd0d","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfe2588a0953f3b64aa50f87c25953d97d5b68b","tid":1278200,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"留名學野<br />\n由南到北?<br />\n唔會北到北海道下話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:14:18.000Z","msg":"係啊, 而家已經離開石垣, 去到水戶<br />\n利申: 今日係Day 5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d87ead736a4f8cdddcd10ca5c56b25f16cb166","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:38:09.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n<br />\n一早起身去巴士總站join bus tour, 俾完錢坐左係度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fxf3EJF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFxf3EJF.jpg&h=a608cd94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行程<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kS7Bfhd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkS7Bfhd.jpg&h=a36dddcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unT1roX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunT1roX.jpg&h=ee5bb912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一站係唐人墓<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%94%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%A2%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2594%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A2%2593&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=a6691dfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%94%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%A2%93</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vvhd1YG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVvhd1YG.jpg&h=24adbd39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去川平灣, 自費坐玻璃船<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/msQWfjk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmsQWfjk.jpg&h=07c946c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7mitEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7mitEv.jpg&h=b84916a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐船中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yeTMCx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyeTMCx3.jpg&h=154e2dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天公作美, 藍天白雲, 水又靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5DwOET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5DwOET.jpg&h=96618545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7S5S6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7S5S6Z.jpg&h=d189908d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n龜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9THNm0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9THNm0v.jpg&h=4b4b7629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n魚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXi8QUc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXi8QUc.jpg&h=00c08c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上岸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLygZNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLygZNQ.jpg&h=00e1b470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvfZXzx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvfZXzx.jpg&h=865e032a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuqnVme.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuqnVme.jpg&h=bce5dc0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實有片, 不過大太可能要遲d先upload <br />\n出門, 待續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc17eabde52e07fc7d49251ae1dd6c2ae948493","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"個tour 包午餐, 一般貨色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/codtbk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcodtbk2.jpg&h=25e2f873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過出面望到個海都幾靚, 加分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6Nmwmv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6Nmwmv.jpg&h=47c204cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽去&quot;米原熱帶原始林&quot;, 落車行左5分鐘, 結果...<br />\n就係行去睇幾顆樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uTMHtO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uTMHtO.jpg&h=b22180b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmqrHtZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcmqrHtZ.jpg&h=11b8b820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住去最後一個景點: 玉取崎, 一上到觀景台, 真係靚到嘩一聲!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBDH0g3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBDH0g3.jpg&h=0390c753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VcURpf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VcURpf.jpg&h=a226a074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wR4DyCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwR4DyCU.jpg&h=32f12443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就上車返車站, 完左個tour啦<br />\n我覺得如果你唔係自駕, 個tour都好值得參加<br />\n<br />\n落左車行返去酒店, 途中見到間朱古力鋪, 入去叫左個tea食<br />\n超好食啊! 間鋪拎過獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srMqX51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrMqX51.jpg&h=0f7ac066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Jm6Hx5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Jm6Hx5.jpg&h=37fa8eee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完book埋觀星就返hostel叉個電<br />\n<br />\n休息左陣就食野去觀星了<br />\n<br />\n觀星無乜好講, 俾錢上船出海, 日本人多, 香港人都有幾個<br />\n<br />\n導遊講日文, 有支laser輔助, 我聽唔明就自已睇了<br />\n<br />\n喺船好難影相, 得一張叫影到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TkwKufc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTkwKufc.jpg&h=46e572d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回程時導遊拎支三線出黎自彈自唱, 其實係咪個個staff都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為幾日都有唔同導遊/ 司機咁樣做<br />\n<br />\n落船就返hostel休息了<br />\n<br />\nDay 2完"},{"pid":"33b092581b684474011e2f64da9d2e24048553d8","tid":1278200,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"I&rsquo;ll be going to Tokyo, Kagoshima and Fukuoka for the summer holiday. I&rsquo;ll bring along a durian 😋"},{"pid":"7a02f66e0d377dc8feae03388b99382be24434d9","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"Day 3<br />\n<br />\n今日行程係西表島&gt;由布島&gt;竹富島<br />\n<br />\n起身去買杯咖啡, 發現珍珠熱潮已經入侵到連便利店都有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rsB26hY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrsB26hY.jpg&h=3de031e6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去counter拎完今日嘅飛之後就上船, 一出海已經見到今日個海好靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDDMOwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDDMOwW.jpg&h=7d6a1f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左西表島就上另一架船遊覽仲間川, 兩岸都係紅樹林<br />\n<br />\n見到d水變左色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOPzXr2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOPzXr2.jpg&h=02218c60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EDfjo64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEDfjo64.jpg&h=e4c46a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始見到d樹, 生得好特別, d根係露喺出面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkcBrmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkcBrmL.jpg&h=ec19185b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jO40S12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjO40S12.jpg&h=026d5e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菠蘿都有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4j8ht0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4j8ht0.jpg&h=dd3c8977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WoUPMot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWoUPMot.jpg&h=221977d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後上一上岸參觀一棵四百歲嘅樹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yXj4Ahn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyXj4Ahn.jpg&h=4b7a5d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nd根生到咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtvrOCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtvrOCv.jpg&h=aeda5a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等開船期間見到紅樹林好常見嘅彈塗魚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/412Nx7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F412Nx7U.jpg&h=f30f447a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該細到睇唔到, crop出黎俾大家睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnA7x75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnA7x75.jpg&h=afbafd68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開船後就上岸坐車再轉水牛車去由布島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2b9TtG9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2b9TtG9.jpg&h=ef9dfa9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水牛車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOY812j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOY812j.jpg&h=839e3be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地真係好鍾意彈三線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eM7JQV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeM7JQV5.jpg&h=6984b23a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由布島, 去西表島基本上一定去埋嘅地方, 但亦係今日最伏嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾大家睇下地圖先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNQCVoH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNQCVoH.jpg&h=a278215e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個園得幾個地方睇, 但係行程係逗留2個鐘(連食飯)<br />\n我到嘅時侯係十一點半, 太陽喺正頭頂, 所以食左飯先<br />\n個午餐幾好食, 仲有碗湯無入鏡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/seypApS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FseypApS.jpg&h=cddff9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經食得好慢, 但仲有個半鐘俾我行, 而天氣係熱到溶, 都唔知點捱...<br />\n本來想餵牛, 點知休息...咁就行去隔離蝴蝶園<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q19grxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq19grxF.jpg&h=5e6ba26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去比出面更熱更焗, 而蝴蝶得兩種...快快趣影幾張走人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZFvv0K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZFvv0K.jpg&h=5626fc73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6EwytNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6EwytNs.jpg&h=b898f66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁熱, 想行去海邊涼下啦, 原來魔鬼魚就係咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HOMONU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HOMONU.jpg&h=a649d9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩間茶屋係真, 買杯雪糕降下溫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3ZL4mt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3ZL4mt.jpg&h=f2feebf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PKBuMz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPKBuMz9.jpg&h=ef970b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k05Z8Ow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk05Z8Ow.jpg&h=5b23bf14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifArOOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifArOOM.jpg&h=08a99658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我架牛車好慢, 俾後面推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vfS2m9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvfS2m9e.jpg&h=ec66641f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落左牛車, 又再上車去碼頭, 瘋狂轉車令我覺得買套票而唔係自已玩係無決定錯<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"ee194f88baae27dd79427e568bdd4f925b6ec868","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"搭船去竹富島, 一落船又再上船, 不過係玻璃船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係睇野同影相嘅時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4xNAsO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4xNAsO.jpg&h=c596090a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHJQyeC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHJQyeC.jpg&h=9fd215da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ix4POOa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fix4POOa.jpg&h=8a888bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後上左架小巴, 去星沙濱搵星沙, 導遊叔叔一搵就搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地成團人搵左好耐都唔係人人成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qhUXdfj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqhUXdfj.jpg&h=a6d51ef2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TS3UfuN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTS3UfuN.jpg&h=efdd1c01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LaGiG9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLaGiG9P.jpg&h=2927be8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去左另一個沙灘, 不過無得落車, 再去左個村仔, 今次就落車行<br />\n十二生肖石, 完全睇唔出個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SV5GEXf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSV5GEXf.jpg&h=73df79fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古董郵筒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9f7Av6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT9f7Av6.jpg&h=9ca80cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度都有水牛車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2E4gtRd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2E4gtRd.jpg&h=26c37aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後去觀景台, 有條路可以行上去不過白色果舊野封左, 聽講可以望到西表島, 不過當日望唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ZsxMDF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ZsxMDF.jpg&h=25821f4e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HT1EZs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HT1EZs.jpg&h=932112d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後坐車回程去碼頭, 上船完結今日嘅行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為間朱古力太好食, 所以去食多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POcxME4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOcxME4.jpg&h=0da3a14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 3完"},{"pid":"b4b23587e60b356749a68a741e2c796b1d4b214e","tid":1278200,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"北到邊？"},{"pid":"ec96fac2180dba35f19629477d3bf8e702f3a181","tid":1278200,"uid":138447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:03:15.000Z","msg":"我4月都去左石垣島，潛水同浮潛好好玩"},{"pid":"2af70178f958b842b0079fde06b5c82ef4d49c53","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4b23587e60b356749a68a741e2c796b1d4b214e","tid":1278200,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"北到邊？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"宗谷岬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d380c63d50df5f1852496e9902ef5580de1e9af","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec96fac2180dba35f19629477d3bf8e702f3a181","tid":1278200,"uid":138447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:03:15.000Z","msg":"我4月都去左石垣島，潛水同浮潛好好玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"我都想玩潛水，不過溝通唔到怕浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338b4e0512709de9e9dfce3448cbe79759e2b1af","tid":1278200,"uid":138447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d380c63d50df5f1852496e9902ef5580de1e9af","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec96fac2180dba35f19629477d3bf8e702f3a181","tid":1278200,"uid":138447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:03:15.000Z","msg":"我4月都去左石垣島，潛水同浮潛好好玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"我都想玩潛水，不過溝通唔到怕浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"教潛水果啲係識講英文嫁，同要學嘅野好簡單<br />\n潛水輕鬆過浮潛好多"},{"pid":"a478e200f7c03c78f4a1229fb9e4169ff85f8492","tid":1278200,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2af70178f958b842b0079fde06b5c82ef4d49c53","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4b23587e60b356749a68a741e