嘅<br />\n<br />\ncheck in完食個lunch, 臨走前食多次石垣牛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ogv0ivZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgv0ivZ.jpg&h=b8a33e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭B787去東京<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWJX5a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbWJX5a8.jpg&h=c73739d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n起飛, 再見啦石垣, 同埋藍到過份嘅海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HcXJ0K0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHcXJ0K0.jpg&h=2b0eca89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次搭, 好大鄉里咁玩佢個窗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3TThkLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3TThkLt.jpg&h=a7eb0ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PdZ4Lcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdZ4Lcb.jpg&h=81a6b8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過接近3個鐘嘅飛行時間, 安全抵達東京, 仲見到架star wars特別版ANA<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWLvFL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWLvFL1.jpg&h=09cc16ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再轉車去水戶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGqLuEB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGqLuEB.jpg&h=b9f79bc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食埋個沾麵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkCBBjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkCBBjH.jpg&h=c875c45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲多罐冰凍啤酒, e隻酒好啱我口味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQA30MB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQA30MB.jpg&h=7260b6ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 4完<br />\n<br />\n今日係無野講, 不過都要照打無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下一日會多d野寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c24610ca7176c0b7bd6ddc1781dda034533ce7","tid":1278200,"uid":96126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"81b5662f3d89a39b616bc2d16b9e57b18e29e61b","tid":1278200,"uid":118069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"Day 5<br />\n<br />\n朝早去麵包鋪買個早餐, 日本好多麵包鋪都有得坐埋噝度食, 麵包檸檬味, 幾特別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGPwBHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGPwBHU.jpg&h=0f6f981d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完行去水戶北口坐巴士去日本三名園之一嘅偕樂園<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PKBu7Qe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPKBu7Qe.jpg&h=0cd1e438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐廿分鐘左右就到, 要行小小路上去東門<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z69TP3S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz69TP3S.jpg&h=fe9cc3bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jpfPooV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjpfPooV.jpg&h=3e0e62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n偕樂園就主要種梅花嘅, 理想情況係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auNViXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauNViXQ.jpg&h=d71a5915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但因為時間唔啱, 所以現實係:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EtdtDX6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEtdtDX6.jpg&h=923f531e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過繡球花就係開花期<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sB3JsSk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsB3JsSk.jpg&h=92115cfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行下影下去到表門, 表門先係正門<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGV0u6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGV0u6z.jpg&h=bd1f48f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正門行去好文亭, 條路左門竹林右面杉樹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZTtD0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZTtD0k.jpg&h=32de1037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EA39or2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEA39or2.jpg&h=f97e14a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吐玉泉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdsmY0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtdsmY0H.jpg&h=31eb047d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到達好文亭, 好文亭係當時d文人聚會嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/znxqGew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FznxqGew.jpg&h=481e316a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識介紹, 自己睇相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHCFu8i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHCFu8i.jpg&h=89633670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ki2RBON.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fki2RBON.jpg&h=608ed740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCZgNVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCZgNVy.jpg&h=dc2c2894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AnkosVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAnkosVE.jpg&h=9aba14a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7w6981.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7w6981.jpg&h=9a6265d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbmrqHo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbmrqHo.jpg&h=e4ac8a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijP4WO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F